{"lemma":"زِرِّ","slug":"زِرِّ","root":"ز.ر.ر","root_slug":"ز-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زِرِّ","root":"زور","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17606","","n17612","n17613","n17614"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to encroach upon one's enemy"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to apprehend, to perceive"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to beam, to dazzle, to gleam, to glitter"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to button"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to collect intensely"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to constrict"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to blanch, to bleach, to dust off"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"button"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"switch button in a power socket"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17606","headword_ar":"زَرَّ","root":"zr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazur~u","text_ar":"يَزُرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~N","text_ar":"زَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He buttoned"},{"kind":"text","text":"a shirt [&c.]; (S, Mgh, Msb, K; *) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zr~r","text_ar":"زرّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazoriyrN","text_ar":"تَزْرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh; [and so in the present day;]) or the latter verb [relates to several objects, or means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he buttoned"},{"kind":"text","text":"a shirt &c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with many buttons;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for it] has an intensive signification. (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Auzoruro","text_ar":"اُزْرُرْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka qamiySaka","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ قَمِيصَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zur~ahu","text_ar":"زُرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zur~ihi","text_ar":"زُرِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zur~uhu","text_ar":"زُرُّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Button upon thee thy shirt."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He narrowed"},{"kind":"text","text":"his eyes [as when one draws together the edges of a vest in buttoning it]. (K, * [in which, in this instance, as in others, only the inf. n. of the verb"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~a","text_ar":"زَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is mentioned,] and TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew together, vehemently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forcibly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, K *) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~ahaA","text_ar":"زَرَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[referring to the pieces of cloth composing a tent]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made in them what are called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraAr","text_ar":"اَزْرَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~N","text_ar":"زِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~a","text_ar":"زَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above, (S, A, TA,) and so the inf. n., (S, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drove away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K, TA. [In the TA, the inf. n. is expl. by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ak~u","text_ar":"الشَّكُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~arodu","text_ar":"الطَّرْدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but the former is a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~al~u","text_ar":"الشَّلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the reading in the S.]) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yazur~u AlkataAy^iba","text_ar":"هُوَ يَزُرُّ الكَتَايِبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAls~ayofi","text_ar":"بِالسَّيْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drives away the troops with the sword."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A.) ―         -b6-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bit"},{"kind":"text","text":"another. (S, * A, K. *) ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pierced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thrust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"another, (K, TA,) with a spear. (TK.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He plucked out"},{"kind":"text","text":"hair. (K, * TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He shook"},{"kind":"text","text":"goods, or household furniture, or the like,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to remove dust &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K: * only the inf. n. is mentioned in the latter.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~a","text_ar":"زَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazir~u","text_ar":"يَزِرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He increased in intelligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and in probations,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"experiences."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zarira","text_ar":"زَرِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below, in this paragraph.])       -A3-  Also, aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazir~u","text_ar":"يَزِرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariyrN","text_ar":"زَرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a spear-head)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleamed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistened."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~ato Eayonuhu","text_ar":"زَرَّتْ عَيْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazir~u","text_ar":"تَزِرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariyrN","text_ar":"زَرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eye gleamed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glistened."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonaAhu tazr~aAni fiY raA^osihi","text_ar":"عَيْنَاهُ تَزرَّانِ فِى رَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eyes gleam,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glisten, in his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, * A, TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zarira","text_ar":"زَرِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiEa","text_ar":"سَمِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [by rule"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~a","text_ar":"زَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", sec. pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zarirota","text_ar":"زَرِرْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazar~u","text_ar":"يَزَرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted wrongfully, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unjustly, to his adversary,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"antagonist."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became intelligent after having been foolish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stupid."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. [See also a signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~a","text_ar":"زَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", above.])"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n17612","headword_ar":"زَرٌّ","root":"zr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~a","text_ar":"زَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, Mgh, Msb, K. *)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~N","text_ar":"زِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17613","headword_ar":"زُرٌّ","root":"zr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17614","headword_ar":"زِرٌّ","root":"zr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K, &c.,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zur~N","text_ar":"زُرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk,) app. in the same sense, (Az,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~N","text_ar":"زَرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been also mentioned, but this is doubtful, (MF,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A button"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, A, Msb, TA) of a shirt, (IAar, S, A, Msb, K,) and of other things, as, for instance, of a curtain: (MF, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loop into which a button is put:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh:) the latter, accord. to Az, is the right meaning: (TA:) [but the former is that to which the word is generally applied:] the former is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziyrN","text_ar":"زِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", by a change of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraArN","text_ar":"اَزْرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuruwrN","text_ar":"زُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) [Hence the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^alozamu liY","text_ar":"هُوَ اَلْزَمُ لِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino zir~iY liEurowatihi","text_ar":"مِنْ زِرِّى لِعُرْوَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is more fast to me than my button to its loop"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTaAniyhi bizir~ihi","text_ar":"اَعْطَانِيهِ بِزِرِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave it to me altogether."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alz~ir~u","text_ar":"الزِّرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ξ","text_ar":"ξ","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of Gemini;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the two stars called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhanoEapu","text_ar":"الهَنْعَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Kzw.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~N","text_ar":"زِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain piece of wood at the upper extremity of the pole of a tent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K: *) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraArN","text_ar":"اَزْرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the upper end of the tent-pole is inserted into it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AzrAr","text_ar":"ازرار"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tent ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xibaA='","text_ar":"خِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":") are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"certain pieces of wood which are sewed into the upper parts of the pieces of cloth which compose the tent, the lower ends of which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of cloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are upon the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zar~ahaA","text_ar":"زَرَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies “ he made in them [namely the said pieces of cloth] such pieces of wood. ” (TA.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"socket in which the head of the upper bone of the arm turns;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K; *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the half of a nut:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head itself of that bone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity of the hip-bone, in the socket."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b5-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain small bone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the half of a nut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, [but this is probably a misplaced insertion, from the A, ubi suprà,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneath the heart, of which it is the support."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b6-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The edge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of the two edges,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) of a sword. (IAar, K, TA.) ―         -b7-  One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lazir~N mino A^azoraAri AlA_ibili","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَزِرٌّ مِنْ اَزْرَارِ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, K *) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is one who keeps close to the camels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a good pastor of them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K. [Accord. to the A, it seems to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~N","text_ar":"زِرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ a button. ”]) You term also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~u maAlK","text_ar":"زِرُّ مَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who drives camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, vehemently;"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to some; but the preceding meaning, given in the K, is the more correct: (TA:) or it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one acquainted with the right management thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who manages them well;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlK","text_ar":"مَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zurozuwru","text_ar":"زُرْزُورُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~u Ald~iyni","text_ar":"زِرُّ الدِّينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The support,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prop, of the religion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Abu-l-'Abbás, K;) like the small bone called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~","text_ar":"زِرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the support of the heart: (Abu-l-'Abbás, TA:) applied, in a trad., to 'Alee: in another relation, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~u AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"زِرُّ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he between whom and the earth is a mutual dependance, and without whose existence one would repudiate the earth and mankind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to Th,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he by whom the earth becomes firm, like as a shirt does by means of its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~","text_ar":"زِرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"button"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["ISk","Az","MF","IAar","A","Msb","TA","S","K","ISh","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}